    "Specifically, the statement \"AI A sees the pain in Person B \" is captured by the function I I YOU see,",
    ", which returns information about the Person B 's pain.",
    "The symbol × represents the Cartesian product of two sets.",
    "Given two sets A and B, the Cartesian product A B × is the set of all ordered pairs a b,",
    "where a is an element of A and b is an element of B."
